{"tid":782640,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Ocamp】陳晚玩一生人一次，原來唔洗除bra","createTime":"2018-08-17T01:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T05:06:21.000Z","uid":11512,"like":13,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3487d184021e49f43b6bbc88772997736bdd6abe","tid":782640,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"邊個就唔講 驚自爆<br />\n咁陳晚就玩一生人一次<br />\n結果玩左差不多成個鐘小妹重未諗到係除眼罩<br />\n又俾隔離啲玩完既人係咁騷擾<br />\n係咁講&quot;嘩！咁大對野包到實一實唔辛苦架咩?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果一時諗錯左連個bra都除埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為小妹都幾大波的<br />\n結果一除果下班友係咁嘩嘩聲同起到笑<br />\n嚇到組爸即刻沖埋黎用手cup住我對波<br />\n可能情急之下快手得濟唔小心渣實左我對波搓左兩野<br />\n<br />\n小妹到而家都唔敢話俾男朋友知<br />\n其實俾組爸搓左兩野之後出左小小水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3525c53fc83c4262661091d82d1ce2803e69c23e","tid":782640,"uid":47268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"系，禾琴日仲除咗底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fe7cf27b680c2f77eab620977e7ef4f0f2bfd5","tid":782640,"uid":201512,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"請善用____功能"},{"pid":"f5ac7b14b581282dfd1099d6de0c150b3303e946","tid":782640,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3525c53fc83c4262661091d82d1ce2803e69c23e","tid":782640,"uid":47268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"系，禾琴日仲除咗底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:03:56.000Z","msg":"組爸有無幫你手?"},{"pid":"bc0b85174d947424a7b00a88b50e061bc26da057","tid":782640,"uid":5163,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"04e6f93a5ed7662933678f2689ca84334c1c63fa","tid":7